Package org.seasar.dbflute.maven.plugin

Class Summary
AbstractDBFluteMojo AbstractDBFluteMojo is a parent Mojo class for maven-dbflute-plugin.
CreateClientPlugin CreateClientPlugin provides create-client goal to create dbflute client.
DocCommandPlugin DocCommandPlugin provides doc goal to run doc.[sh|bat].
DownloadPlugin Download Plugin provides download goal to download a zip file of dbflute.
GenerateCommandPlugin GenerateCommandPlugin provides generate goal to run generate.[sh|bat].
GenerateCrudPlugin GenerateCrudPlugin provides generate-crud goal to generate CRUD pages.
GenerateCrudPropertyPlugin GenerateCrudPlugin provides generate-crud goal to generate CRUD pages.

ReplaceSchemaCommandPlugin ReplaceSchemaCommandPlugin provides replace-schema goal to run replace-schema.[sh|bat].
Sql2entityCommandPlugin Sql2entityCommandPlugin provides sql2entity goal to run sql2entity.[sh|bat].
UpgradePlugin UpgradePlugin provides upgrade goal to download a zip file of dbflute and replace _project.*.
